      OF THE SITE OR SOFTWARE, WHETHER IN CONTRACT, TORT, OR OTHERWISE, EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE
      POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="lp-section" id="third-parties">
    <h2><span class="lp-num">07</span><a href="#third-parties">Third parties</a></h2>
    <p>
      The Site links to third-party services such as GitHub and our documentation host. We are not
      responsible for the content, policies, or practices of any third-party site, and accessing
      them is at your own risk under their terms.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="lp-section" id="indemnification">
